@startuml
actor User
participant CLI
participant DeepSeek
participant BayesianQA
participant Transformer
participant HFSpaces

User -> CLI: query(question)
CLI -> DeepSeek: embed & retrieve top_k
DeepSeek -> CLI: docs + embeddings
CLI -> BayesianQA: compute posterior
BayesianQA -> CLI: best_answer + confidence
alt confidence < threshold
  CLI -> Transformer: generate(question)
  Transformer -> CLI: generated_answer
end
CLI -> HFSpaces: (optionally log or deploy)
CLI -> User: return answer
@enduml
